# This file is NOT used in production.
# All values are injected via GitHub Actions Secrets → ci-write-remote-logging-env.sh.
#
# Required GitHub Secrets:
#   LOGGING_ELASTIC_PASSWORD     — Elasticsearch superuser password
#
# Optional GitHub Secrets (fallback to LOGGING_ELASTIC_PASSWORD if not set):
#   LOGGING_ADMIN_PASSWORD       — Kibana login password (user: admin)
#   LOGGING_KIBANA_SYSTEM_PASSWORD — kibana_system backend password
#   LOGGING_KIBANA_HOST          — default: kibana.dsp5-archi-o22a-15m-g3.fr
#
# For local dev only (copy to .env and fill):
# KIBANA_HOST=kibana.dsp5-archi-o22a-15m-g3.fr
# ELASTIC_PASSWORD=
# KIBANA_SYSTEM_PASSWORD=
# KIBANA_USERNAME=admin
# KIBANA_PASSWORD=
